            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">96. A man with atypical chest pain is found to have normal nuclear isotope uptake in his myocardium at rest. On exercise, there is decreased uptake in the inferior wall. Two hours after exercise, the uptake of nuclear isotope returns to normal. What is the right thing to do?</p>"
